  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink61-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vatuvaiyayarntāḷ oru parattaiyaic ciṉṉāḷil viṭṭu maṟṟoru parattaiyai
          vatuvaiyayarntāṉ ‘eṉpatu aṟinta talaimakaḷ avaṉ maṉaivayiṟ pukkuḻip pulantāḷāka, ‘itu
          maṟaittaṟku aritu’ eṉa uṭaṉpaṭṭu, iṉi eṉṉiṭattu ivvāṟu nikaḻātu’ eṉṟāṟku avaḷ colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink61">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>naṟuvaṭi māattu viḷaintuku tīmpaḻa</l>
          <l>neṭunīrp poykait tuṭumeṉa viḻūuṅ</l>
          <l>kaivaṇ matti kaḻāa raṉṉa</l>
          <l>nallōr nallōr nāṭi</l>
          <l>vatuvai yayara virumputi nīyē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


          <l> These good women like Kaḻār,</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> [the city] of Matti, the liberal of hand, </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> where sweet fruit, ripened </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> and shed by the mango tree </l>
          <l rend="indent6">with its fragrant, tender green fruit</l> 
          <l rend="indent8"> fall into the wide waters of the pond with a splash – </l>
          <p/>
          <l> picking through these good women one after another, </l>
          <l> you want to marry them [all]. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
